\lim_{n\to \infty }a_n=L 
m_n=\frac{\sum_{1}^{n}a_k}{n}
\lim m_n=L
\sum_{1}^{n}a_k=na_k
m_n=\frac{\sum_{1}^{n}a_k}{n}=\frac{na_k}{n}=a_k
\lim a_k=L.\square
